*Sprat*u je trebalo da bude gotov za tri nedelje (The floor had to be finished in three weeks).

Ulica je dugačka i ima mnogo *spratova* (The street is long and has many floors).

Kada je uselila u novi stan bila je prezadovoljna jer je imao četiri *sprata* (When she moved into a new apartment she was very pleased because it had four floors).

Prodavnica je bila na drugom *spratu* (The store was on the second floor).

Ovaj zgrada je visok tri *sprata* (This building is three floors high).

Posetili smo *sprat* sa muzejom (We visited the floor with the museum).